comment: An Axiom of Choice equivalent: there exists a function ` f ` (called a choice function) with domain ` A ` that maps each nonempty member of the domain to an element of that member. Axiom AC of [BellMachover] p. 488. Note that the assertion that ` f ` be a function is not necessary; see ~ ac4 . (Contributed by NM, 29-Aug-1999.)
